            "itemType": "journalArticle",
            "title": "Macrophyllum macrophyllum (CHIROPTERA, PHYLLOSTOMIDAE) IN THE BRAZILIAN CAATINGA SCRUBLANDS: RIVER BASINS AS POTENTIAL ROUTES OF DISPERSAL IN XERIC ECOSYSTEMS",
            "creators": [
